% ********************************************************************************
%
% Figure 7.6(a) from the book: "The Theory of the Moire Phenomenon"
% by I. Amidror, published by Kluwer Academic Publishers, 1999.
%
%		* * *  Copyright (c) 1999 EPFL  * * *
